The paper discusses a solution to the problem of centralization in blockchain networks due to the large amount of data to be stored, which is a common issue in distributed computing and networking. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
